{% comment %} Nootropix — TL;DR bullets (Premium) {% endcomment %}
{%- assign s = section.settings -%}
{%- assign sid = section.id -%}
{%- assign alpha = s.alpha_gpc -%}
{%- assign cdp = s.cdp_choline -%}

{%- style -%}
#nx-tldr-{{ sid }} {
  --nx-accent-glass: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.08);
  --nx-accent-dark: var(--color-accent-dark, #92400e);
  --nx-text: var(--color-text-main, #111827);
  --nx-muted: var(--color-text-muted, #4b5563);
  --nx-radius: var(--radius-premium, 14px);
  --nx-transition: var(--transition-premium, all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1));
  --nx-shadow-rest: var(--shadow-sm, 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04));
  --nx-font: var(--font-body-family, sans-serif);
  --nx-font-heading: var(--font-heading-family, sans-serif);

  max-width: var(--container-width-narrow);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 8px 16px 0;
  font-family: var(--nx-font);
  color: var(--nx-text);
  line-height: 1.6;
  content-visibility: auto;
}

#nx-tldr-{{ sid }} h2 {
  font-family: var(--nx-font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin: 0 0 16px;
}

#nx-tldr-{{ sid }} .nx-tldr-card {
  background: rgba(249, 250, 251, 0.65);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  border-radius: var(--nx-radius);
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  box-shadow: var(--nx-shadow-rest);
  padding: 20px 24px;
  transition: var(--nx-transition);
}
#nx-tldr-{{ sid }} .nx-tldr-card:hover {
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md, 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.06));
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

#nx-tldr-{{ sid }} ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; }
#nx-tldr-{{ sid }} li { margin: 8px 0; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--nx-muted); }
#nx-tldr-{{ sid }} li strong { color: var(--nx-text); }

#nx-tldr-{{ sid }} a:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-accent-primary, #FBBF24);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  #nx-tldr-{{ sid }},
  #nx-tldr-{{ sid }} * {
    transition: none !important;
    animation: none !important;
    transform: none !important;
  }
}
{%- endstyle -%}

<section id="nx-tldr-{{ sid }}" aria-label="Key takeaways">
  <h2>TL;DR (Key Takeaways)</h2>
  <div class="nx-tldr-card">
    <ul>
      <li>We focus on what's <strong>in stock</strong>: Aniracetam, Fasoracetam, Phenylpiracetam Hydrazide, Pramiracetam — plus powder options.</li>
      <li>Use cases differ: <strong>Aniracetam</strong> (fast focus + mood), <strong>Fasoracetam</strong> (calm focus), <strong>Phenylpiracetam Hydrazide</strong> (peak days), <strong>Pramiracetam</strong> (long retention).</li>
      <li>Most stacks pair racetams with a <strong>choline donor</strong>{% if alpha != blank or cdp != blank %} — {{ alpha.title | default: 'Alpha-GPC' }} or {{ cdp.title | default: 'CDP-Choline' }}{% endif %}.</li>
      <li>Start low, assess response; consider targeted (as-needed) use.</li>
      <li>Athletes: phenylpiracetam-class compounds may be restricted — check your federation.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "NX — TL;DR",
  "settings": [
    { "type": "product", "id": "alpha_gpc", "label": "Alpha-GPC (optional)" },
    { "type": "product", "id": "cdp_choline", "label": "CDP-Choline (optional)" }
  ],
  "presets": [{ "name": "NX — TL;DR" }]
}
{% endschema %}
